data.description: **Welcome to 330 Emporia Loop!! This home is in PRISTINE condition! (Like New) Upgrades Galore, open Floor concept! large entertaining area , chefs DREAM kitchen with tons of counter space and cabinets, 2 pantry closets. A  large guest bedroom downstairs with a full bathroom! Master is huge with walk in closet and Beautiful ensuite. 3 more Large bedrooms and Big closets . Hardwood floors, tile and granite! Partial fenced in yard with plenty of space to play, a security system, a community pool, tennis court and basketball court! A must see. Call for details and showings!
